{"tid":732761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★創業失敗孭債 23歲仔車內燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-07-07T07:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T11:23:45.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9856732883dfb9fe8fac986bbb3fb40562fedfe9","tid":732761,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:42:30.000Z","msg":"姓李（廿三歲）事主未婚，在上水金錢村居住。據悉，他曾在內地<span style=\"color: red;\">經營電子生意</span>，惟生意失敗欠債，令他精神飽受壓力。昨凌晨零時許，李向胞兄及友人發出死亡短訊，聲稱在大帽山燒炭自殺，各人聞訊報警求助。警方趕往大帽山一帶搜索，但未有發現。直至凌晨四時許，警員在事主住所附近空地上，發現其掛上中港牌的私家車，李昏迷車內及有盆燒過的炭，消防員趕至擊破車窗，將李救出，惟送院後，證實不治。警方調查後，不排除事主因金錢問題困擾萌死。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180707/00176_072.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180707%2F00176_072.html&d=wN71S7GrUjmYvKgdS9wyd7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=94df9698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180707/00176_072.html</a>"},{"pid":"d1b58c19c8d76b346d711b212ddc0672bba209d3","tid":732761,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:42:48.000Z","msg":"經營電子生意=IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b9676f165546896eaebcb08409f9d7421db491","tid":732761,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"老綜 = 必賺"},{"pid":"88d2df6ca7ff6cc03943bd13722157fc33efdc39","tid":732761,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:44:07.000Z","msg":"在<span style=\"color: red;\">內地</span>經營電子生意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nchi na"},{"pid":"3165183c1a9e98e2a15d8c566e0ff44ee69ae689","tid":732761,"uid":8410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T07:44:40.000Z","msg":"見唔對路就del game 重玩"},{"pid":"348f9687fe9338136b92c833b47715cee7d9d3ff","tid":732761,"uid":26752,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9856732883dfb9fe8fac986bbb3fb40562fedfe9","tid":732761,"uid":194